name: OG Astro – Inner Nature
description:
A piece of digital art history. Here, in
an endless NFT rotation, "The OG
Astro" contemplates their Inner
nature. A rare, single piece, this work
explores the notions of solitude, the
affirmation of nature and the acute
repetitiveness of the modern
condition. Small details are hidden in
the work that reward viewers on
repeat viewings
